body:
## Warning: **n00bneSS!!**
I have no idea what I'm doing with git so if someone gets offended, suck it up _(or better yet, tell me how to do it properly)._

### Original Repository:
* **root**: andymatuschak
* **name**: NSObject-AssociatedObjects

```
> $ cd your_repo_root/repo_name
> $ git fetch origin
> $ git checkout gh-pages
```

The method I used was via “GitHub.app” for OSX. I forked a version for myself and cloned it so I can seriously screw around with it. I'll commit whenever I save but won't ever click pull, merge, or any other button of unknown consequences.

**_— Aesthir_**
